reviewText: I was in this movie so what else would you expect but an excellent review.....Academy Award material.....don't miss this fine film!

Different, cute, funny and like able. A bit over dramatic and sometimes movement too choppy...no flow.  I would watch it again as it is about a daughter who had her own interests that weren't like her rich family. A good family, however, image was important...which she did more good for the family than not until they found out...... En espanol
